
<acqabr>DNA MEDICAL</acqabr> {<acqcode>DNAM</acqcode>} SIGNS PACT FOR STOCK SALE
    SALT LAKE CITY, March 16 - <acquired>DNA Medical Inc</acquired> said <purchaser>Walter G.
Mize</purchaser> had bought about 9,400,000 shares, or about 33 pct of
<acqabr>DNA</acqabr>'s outstanding stock, for 100,000 dlrs cash.
    Under an agreement with <purchabr>Mize</purchabr>, <acqabr>DNA</acqabr> said he will also become
chairman, and may, at his option, expand the board to provide
him equal representation with the current board.
    <acqabr>DNA</acqabr> also said it will submit a proposal at its annual
